{"word":"χορεία","slug":"χορεία","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>χορεία</b></el> <el>(χορεία, ἡ,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:χορεύω'><el>χορεύω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a dance</i>, <a href='S:especially'>esp.</a> <i>the choral</i> or <i>round dance with its music</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a dance tune</i>, <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}